          <div class="mb-10">
            <label class="block text-white font-bold mb-1 font-industrial">1. Qual a porcentagem exata de conversas de vendas que sua diretoria audita hoje?</label>
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500 mb-4 block uppercase tracking-wider">Selecione uma opção</span>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 border border-gray-800 hover:border-gray-600 cursor-pointer transition-colors">
                <input type="radio" name="q1" class="accent-yellow-500 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-gray-700" required>
                <span class="text-gray-400">100%</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 border border-gray-800 hover:border-gray-600 cursor-pointer transition-colors">
